ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgreement with Prince Edward Island - Agricultural Disaster Relief Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to ENTER INTO AN AGREEMENT WITH PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND to provide federal contributions of up to $9,360,000 under the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program to assist affected agricultural producers with the extraordinary costs related to the excess moisture and cold temperatures experienced during the 2018 harvest.
